channel.title: How do i fix this?
channel.description:
I run the server of my RSPS and I get this message.
IT OPENS AND CLOSES WITHIN 1 SECOND. IT TOOK ME A LONG TIME TO GET A CLEAR SCREENSHOT OF IT.
[img]http://speedcap.net/img/d9a4bc56235a9fc1e61427d992a0111f/e6142987.png[/img]
Just wondering how I can fix this problem.
This is what the notepad shows: [img]http://speedcap.net/img/d9a4bc56235a9fc1e61427d992a0111f/044f9999.png[/img]

item.title: How do i fix this?
item.dc:creator: @zadijakas zadijakas
item.description:
@zadijakas wrote:

Clear this text and put this text:
@echo off
“C:/Program Files/Java/jre7/bin/java.exe” -Xmx815m -cp bin;lib/*; com.rs.Launcher true true false
pause
